1 class="mb-6 text-center uppercase xs:text-start">Dive</h1><p class="mb-10 text-center text-lg xs:text-start">Immerse yourself in the wonders of the underwater world. With close proximity to stunning dive sites and a rich variety of marine life, every dive with Azure will surely be an unforgettable adventure.</p><a href="/dive-with-azure"><button class="rounded-full border px-6 py-2 text-center text-[20px] font-semibold transition-colors border-ocean-blue bg-sand text-ocean-blue hover:bg-pale-blue self-stretch xs:self-auto bg-transparent hover:bg-sand">Discover diving spots &amp; lessons</button></a></div></div><img src="/wp-content/themes/azure-dive-resort-2024-wp/media/topographic-2.svg" alt="" class="pointer-events-none absolute bottom-[-135%] left-[55%] z-[1] hidden h-[250%] w-[250%] rotate-180 object-contain opacity-10 xs:block"/></div><div class="relative grid grid-cols-1 justify-items-center overflow-clip xs:grid-cols-2 xs:gap-10 sm:gap-16 md:gap-22.5 2xl:gap-45 bg-sand"><img src="/wp-content/themes/azure-dive-resort-2024-wp/media/landing/dine.jpg" alt="Dine" class="top-header z-[2] h-[600px] w-full object-cover object-center xs:sticky xs:h-screen-noheader"/><div class="z-[2] flex flex-col items-start justify-center justify-self-start px-10 pb-20 pt-10 xs:min-h-[calc(1.5*var(--h-screen-noheader))] xs:py-10 xs:pl-0 xs:pr-10 sm:gap-16 md:pr-22.5 2xl:pr-45"><div class="flex max-w-[560px] flex-col items-center xs:items-start"><h1 class="mb-6 text-center uppercase xs:text-start">Dine</h1><p class="mb-10 text-center text-lg xs:text-start">Beatriz is an all-day dining semi-al fresco restaurant offering a well curated menu of delightful dishes with elegant sea, pool and garden views. Starting early, our breakfast features international and local favorites and healthy options. For lunch and dinner, an inspired menu draws on cuisines from around the world.</p><a href="/beatriz-restaurant"><button class="rounded-full border px-6 py-2 text-center text-[20px] font-semibold transition-colors border-ocean-blue bg-sand text-ocean-blue hover:bg-pale-blue self-stretch xs:self-auto bg-transparent">Learn more about Beatriz Restaurant</button></a></div></div><img src="/wp-content/themes/azure-dive-resort-2024-wp/media/topographic-2.svg" alt="" class="pointer-events-none absolute bottom-[-95%] left-[-2%] z-[1] hidden h-[200%] w-[200%] object-contain opacity-10 xs:block"/></div><div class="relative grid grid-cols-1 justify-items-center overflow-clip xs:grid-cols-2 xs:gap-10 sm:gap-16 md:gap-22.5 2xl:gap-45 bg-pale-blue"><img src="/wp-content/themes/azure-dive-resort-2024-wp/media/landing/relax.jpg" alt="Relax" class="top-header z-[2] h-[600px] w-full object-cover object-center xs:sticky xs:h-screen-noheader"/><div class="z-[2] flex flex-col items-start justify-center justify-self-start px-10 pb-20 pt-10 xs:min-h-[calc(1.5*var(--h-screen-noheader))] xs:py-10 xs:pl-0 xs:pr-10 sm:gap-16 md:pr-22.5 2xl:pr-45"><div class="flex max-w-[560px] flex-col items-center xs:items-start"><h1 class="mb-6 text-center uppercase xs:text-start">Relax</h1><p class="mb-10 text-center text-lg xs:text-start">Whether you’re a diver or just someone looking for some peace and quiet by the beach, Azure is the place to be. Relax by the pool, retreat to our cozy, Filipino-inspired rooms, or savor the calming ocean breeze. Every moment is yours to enjoy.</p><a href="/the-resort"><button class="rounded-full border px-6 py-2 text-center text-[20px] font-semibold transition-colors border-ocean-blue bg-sand text-ocean-blue hover:bg-pale-blue self-stretch xs:self-auto bg-transparent hover:bg-sand">View rooms</button></a></div></div><img src="/wp-content/themes/azure-dive-resort-2024-wp/media/topographic-2.svg" alt="" class="pointer-events-none absolute bottom-[-100%] left-[-5%] z-[1] hidden h-[200%] w-[200%] object-contain opacity-10 xs:block"/></div></section><section class="px-8 py-16 sm:py-22.5"><div class="mx-auto max-w-content"><p class="mb-4 text-center text-overline-big sm:mb-5 sm:text-overline opacity-0">Events and Celebrations</p><h2 class="mb-10 text-center sm:mb-15 opacity-0">Making moments you’ll treasure</h2><div class="grid gap-x-6 gap-y-12 xs:grid-cols-3"><div class="flex flex-col gap-6 opacity-0"><img src="/wp-content/themes/azure-dive-resort-2024-wp/media/landing/events-1.jpg" alt="Weddings" class="h-[500px] w-full object-cover object-center rounded-tr-[200px]"/><div class="grow"><h4 class="mb-3">Weddings</h4><p class="text-lg">Create unforgettable memories with your dreamy beach wedding at Azure. Let our specialized team of wedding stylists and coordinators help you craft your dream wedding in a way that suits your style.</p></div><a class="w-fit" target="_blank" href="mailto:reserveazure@gmail.com?subject=Request for quotation&amp;body=Dear Azure,%0D%0A%0D%0AI would like to request a quotation from your resort.%0D%0A%0D%0AName: %0D%0AContact number: %0D%0ACountry: %0D%0ANationality: %0D%0ADate and time of reservation: %0D%0ANumber of rooms: %0D%0ANumber of guests: %0D%0AEvent (i.e., vacation, wedding, meeting, etc.): %0D%0AOther requests: %0D%0A%0D%0AThank you!"><button class="rounded-full border px-6 py-2 text-center text-[20px] font-semibold transition-colors border-ocean-blue bg-sand text-ocean-blue hover:bg-pale-blue w-fit">Request proposal</button></a></div><div class="flex flex-col gap-6 opacity-0"><img src="/wp-content/themes/azure-dive-resort-2024-wp/media/landing/events-2.jpg" alt="Celebrations Made with Meaning" class="h-[500px] w-full object-cover object-center rounded-t-[200px] object-[53.5%_center]"/><div class="grow"><h4 class="mb-3">Celebrations Made with Meaning</h4><p class="text-lg">Whether it’s a grandiose affair or an intimate birthday or milestone celebration, simplify your planning with meticulously customized packages created for you by our event specialists.</p></div><a class="w-fit" target="_blank" href="mailto:reserveazure@gmail.com?subject=Request for quotation&amp;body=Dear Azure,%0D%0A%0D%0